    metaTitle: "What to Expect at a Reveal Assessment | Rani Beauty Clinic Renton",
    metaDescription: "Curious about our Reveal Assessment for post-weight-loss skin? Walk through exactly what happens during your first visit at Rani Beauty Clinic.",
